Setting Up Our Code Editor
-----------------------------------
We will use vs code. There are alternatives to vscode like Adam, Brackets.

Theme
-------
Extension Symbol---> Click on it and install Monokai pro (However it is paid color theme)

	Another theme that is similar to Monokai Pro is Monokai classic which is free. 
	
VS Code Settings
----------------------
	.AutoSave
		.On FocusChange
Multiu Cursor Modifier
	alt
Word Wrap
	On
Format On Save
	Check
File Icon Theme
	Seti(Visual Studio Code)	
